Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.19,0:00:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蛮勇吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.91,0:00:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或者是在找死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.54,0:00:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)\pos(1075,575)\blur1\bord2.5}白银的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.41,0:00:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,准将 如何处理
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.56,0:00:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,立刻回收指挥机
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.71,0:00:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左文字
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.99,0:00:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让一让 让一让
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.10,0:00:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们哪部分的?不要出长城
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.43,0:00:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们是独立第八部队
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.33,0:00:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,独立第八部队?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.25,0:00:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要前去营救昔日长官 左文字雨京大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.00,0:00:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请多包涵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.24,0:00:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自作主张
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.43,0:00:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是很感人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.12,0:00:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞧他说的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.23,0:00:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说那种话不要紧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.64,0:00:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如今这状况只能靠气势
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.43,0:00:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.55,0:00:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第八部队请回答
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.99,0:01:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阻止左文字雨京 这是命令
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.78,0:01:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.25,0:01:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,混小子居然打红眼了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.34,0:01:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宰了他也得抢回来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.04,0:01:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.57,0:01:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟上独立第八部队
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.78,0:01:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能让夺回长城的英雄白白送死
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.94,0:01:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,救出左文字
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.09,0:01:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,满嘴谎话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.56,0:01:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.05,0:01:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但这状况 我要利用一下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.60,0:01:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,攻击?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.68,0:01:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敌人不是撤退了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.58,0:01:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,友军也开始攻击了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.44,0:01:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.10,0:01:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没你们的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.80,0:01:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,银色歼灭者 你在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.13,0:01:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除我和你们之外都是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.23,0:01:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全员各自为战
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.95,0:02:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到了 是银歼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.11,0:02:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别大意 时宗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.65,0:02:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢 希尔菲小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.43,0:02:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也在哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.09,0:02:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的对手在这呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.19,0:02:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,银歼 已注意到我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.28,0:02:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.22,0:02:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,茜 要是没机会吃饭还请多包涵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.18,0:02:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行 这个没门
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.71,0:02:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.28,0:02:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想吃意面 以上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.31,0:02:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为母则强?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.49,0:02:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经为母了?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.64,0:02:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,按时宗的节奏 该进白刃战了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.86,0:02:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.45,0:02:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拔刀了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.74,0:02:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要相信他的单纯 看你的了帅哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.05,0:02:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,意面 意面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.27,0:02:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,时宗君第一招会{\rsymbol}…{\r}冲头来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.84,0:03:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.60,0:03:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趁现在 劳伦斯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.04,0:03:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,劳伦斯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.17,0:03:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.14,0:03:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快 时宗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.74,0:03:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.38,0:03:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.30,0:03:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,学长 看我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.53,0:03:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奈美惠?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.82,0:03:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再补一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.13,0:03:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,劳伦斯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.87,0:03:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.09,0:03:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快 我们也撑不久
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.67,0:03:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给我老实听话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.34,0:04:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.26,0:04:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,顶住啊 劳伦斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.47,0:04:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,意面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.47,0:04:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉米{\rsymbol}·{\r}哈兹福特
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.90,0:04:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辨识密码 0612 0530
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.25,0:04:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,确认启动认证
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.76,0:04:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.35,0:04:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,转写 吉米{\rsymbol}·{\r}哈兹福特
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.47,0:04:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接入
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.84,0:04:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和上次看的不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.87,0:04:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不对 来看我 看我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.89,0:04:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看着我 银色歼灭者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.86,0:05:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,学长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.93,0:05:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了时宗 尽情冲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.77,0:05:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉米小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.85,0:05:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉米小姐 奈美惠小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.63,0:05:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快过来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.55,0:05:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,军曹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.22,0:05:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪 银色歼灭者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.66,0:05:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.21,0:05:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是银色歼灭者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.84,0:06:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫里希特霍芬来 就是为了这一刻?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.74,0:06:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.34,0:06:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概不论战局如何 我都想成全那家伙完成自己的本愿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.44,0:06:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会在这见证 直到您的最后一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.89,0:06:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即刻起 诱敌深入 开始进一步包围
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.50,0:06:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 不是找你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.42,0:06:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪 左文字先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.65,0:06:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特殊工兵部队联络 即将与指挥机接触
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.26,0:06:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哼 真讽刺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.80,0:06:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,越是指挥大部队 你的机体越像木头
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.61,0:07:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.45,0:07:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左文字先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.85,0:07:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.21,0:07:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪 银色歼灭者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.38,0:07:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.86,0:07:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左文字先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.16,0:07:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诱捕器 激活
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.58,0:07:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那小子{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.20,0:07:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 你小子想寻死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.91,0:07:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,准将 大事不好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.38,0:07:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.34,0:07:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,后方有大部队接近 推测是镇压部队
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.09,0:07:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,泉大佐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.83,0:08:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又来了 又要被剥离出去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.30,0:08:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绝不交给任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.38,0:08:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Link系统 白银的意志 是丽华心愿的终点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.09,0:08:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.79,0:08:18.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它以这个形式{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.99,0:08:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看吧 这个战场
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.67,0:08:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,丽华在最后的实验前对我说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.68,0:08:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\rsymbol2}「{\r}看着我{\rsymbol2}」{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.47,0:08:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 没等我去面对 她就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.74,0:08:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以白银的意志到最后{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.06,0:08:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到最后一刻都要由我见证
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.87,0:08:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从银色歼灭者上下来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.55,0:09:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看不见
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.20,0:09:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,时宗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.03,0:09:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,时宗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.59,0:09:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,时宗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.16,0:09:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在磨蹭什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.35,0:09:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子 是属于你和我的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.19,0:09:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相信它去战斗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.25,0:09:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.49,0:09:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能只是看着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.22,0:09:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得伸手抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.40,0:09:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,银色歼灭者 你 是属于我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.88,0:10:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么能动
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.62,0:10:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是个大蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.11,0:10:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多亏你我们才活到今天
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.92,0:10:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或许战场真的很丑恶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.80,0:10:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 多亏有你我才能融入部队
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.64,0:10:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才觉得自己找到了归宿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.58,0:10:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你却要做这种事?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.23,0:10:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.78,0:10:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了姐姐?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.79,0:10:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 不对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.64,0:10:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你做的事只是自私
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.78,0:10:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了这种事 少拿出姐姐的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.96,0:10:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少特么提我姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.94,0:11:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左文字队长 到此结束吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.43,0:11:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.74,0:11:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,结束吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.04,0:11:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.97,0:11:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.20,0:11:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白银的意志 所有U-Link系统即刻死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.99,0:11:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,与我们一起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.37,0:11:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.63,0:11:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.73,0:11:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会失去一切
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.19,0:12:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要 快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.41,0:12:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.63,0:12:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我遵守了诺言
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.57,0:12:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很快就去找你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.78,0:12:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愿意 看着我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.16,0:12:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,选择了自尽吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.49,0:12:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中央发来指令 要求一时休战
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.29,0:12:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,准备真周到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.84,0:12:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下令撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.36,0:12:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.81,0:12:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我的宏图{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.25,0:13:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一度点燃的火 可没那么容易熄灭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.89,0:13:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愿随您左右
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.39,0:13:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.39,0:13:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.72,0:13:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不得不死
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.40,0:13:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知为何满脑都是这想法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.58,0:13:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特别痛苦 特别孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.62,0:13:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉自己要消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.09,0:14:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 没有消失
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.34,0:14:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那里面有我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.72,0:14:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.90,0:14:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有吉米
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.60,0:14:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.51,0:14:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.04,0:15:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哟 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.26,0:15:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的部队被泉打败 溃不成军
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.66,0:15:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因戈尔米亚也撤军了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.19,0:15:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你和泉的计划成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.88,0:15:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽说你的真正目的 又另在他处
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.24,0:15:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,结果我们 只是被迫看你和南条丽华的殉情大戏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.41,0:15:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.22,0:15:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对想寻死的你 这可能算是慈悲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.55,0:15:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这一琢磨我都不想开枪了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.13,0:15:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但公私要分明
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.22,0:16:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在 请进
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.15,0:16:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行李装好没?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.82,0:16:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.71,0:16:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重启银色歼灭者时 我体会到好多东西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.63,0:16:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能接受吉米的思绪 我很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.84,0:17:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,面对一个人原来是这种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.31,0:17:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,越川说开卡车从这边绕一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.14,0:17:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样好吗 我和军队都没关系了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.88,0:17:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更重要的是你今后怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.06,0:17:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯贝尔尼斯倒闭了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.94,0:17:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 说没就没了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.75,0:17:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 反正没了银色歼灭者我也没工作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.96,0:17:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯? 是谁啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.18,0:17:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.68,0:17:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.46,0:17:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胜吕先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.48,0:17:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说啥来啥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.40,0:17:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好 我是哈兹福特
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.97,0:17:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 抱歉 事后处理脱不开身
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.16,0:17:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,时间不长但辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.87,0:17:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,离职金给你汇过去 记得查收一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.13,0:17:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.95,0:17:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.88,0:17:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唉 离职金
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.79,0:17:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.79,0:17:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯? 多少?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.68,0:17:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.97,0:18:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,汇款搞错了三位数 嘛无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.71,0:18:03.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.20,0:18:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 副产物也出了不少 就这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.80,0:18:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得想想下一个公司的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.69,0:18:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人情我还了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.65,0:18:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会继续盯着韦尔德利贝尔特的动向
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.35,0:18:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.56,0:18:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白银的意志是没了 但系统构想目前还留着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.31,0:18:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左文字在系统中 好像见到了丽华
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.28,0:18:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这有可能吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.62,0:18:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.42,0:18:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他说看到就当看到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.70,0:18:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是他心中白银的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.24,0:18:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,元帅的处分是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.55,0:18:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,处分?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.08,0:18:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左文字是夺回长城的功臣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.83,0:18:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有人把死去的海燕准将看做英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.25,0:18:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有授勋但也不会定罪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.19,0:19:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 我就是讨厌军队这点才不干的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.92,0:19:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么 元帅的战争还会继续咯?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.62,0:19:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.48,0:19:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还得让左文字走一条更艰苦的路
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.23,0:19:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这也是他想要的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.59,0:19:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说不准{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.35,0:19:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.19,0:19:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真正当元帅的 可能会是你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.39,0:19:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 麻烦您了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.44,0:19:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在还这么见外
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.89,0:19:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是嘛 到王都前都顺路
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.62,0:19:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞧我说吧 你想太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.84,0:19:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,话是这么说{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.30,0:19:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,结果新工作决定去哪?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.13,0:19:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总之 先去柯贝尔尼斯竞争对手们那边看看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.08,0:19:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以拿经验丰富当卖点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.78,0:19:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,军队整备兵随时欢迎你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.32,0:19:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟人手不足
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.79,0:19:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是最后的保险
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.85,0:20:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人离心不离也很重要嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.75,0:20:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诶 什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.44,0:20:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全员都准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.91,0:20:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊对了 稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.20,0:20:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.00,0:20:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.23,0:20:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.21,0:20:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这边也准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.20,0:20:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里是席加
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.73,0:20:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路线确认 没有异常
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.39,0:20:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全员 准备完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.42,0:20:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么 出发
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.21,0:21:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,几个月后 阿兰达斯与因戈尔米亚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.52,0:21:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,缔结了停战协定和互不侵犯条约
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.07,0:21:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,互换联络官 规定互相开放情报
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.95,0:21:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但很明显 这只不过是表面上的和平
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.45,0:21:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿兰达斯的联络官已经抵达
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.82,0:21:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很快就到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.50,0:21:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.01,0:21:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过真是有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.62,0:21:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.51,0:21:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来阿兰达斯军中也不乏有想法的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.07,0:21:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知是用做弃子 还是做狮子身中虫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.90,0:21:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不论如何 我都会利用到骨髓
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.11,0:21:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿兰达斯军 联络官阁下带到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.25,0:21:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请他进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.34,0:21:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿兰达斯军少佐 左文字雨京
